00062 bool KX_SCA_EndObjectActuator::Update()
00063 {
00064     // bool result = false; /*unused*/
00065     bool bNegativeEvent = IsNegativeEvent();
00066     RemoveAllEvents();
00067 
00068     if (bNegativeEvent)
00069         return false; // do nothing on negative events
00070     m_scene->DelayedRemoveObject(GetParent());
00071     
00072     return false;
00073 }
